  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="24" y="34" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Risk does not vanish — it migrates. Tokenization's reshuffle</text>
    <text x="24" y="58" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">The buffer of legacy settlement (T+2) vs the immediacy of atomic settlement</text>
    <g font-family="sans-serif">
      <rect x="28" y="82" width="300" height="150" rx="10" fill="#161616" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      <text x="178" y="108" fill="#e4e4e7" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Traditional (T+1 / T+2)</text>
      <text x="178" y="134" fill="#a1a1aa" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Trade → (buffer) → Settle</text>
      <text x="178" y="158" fill="#5eead4" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Margin · netting · reversal</text>
      <text x="178" y="182" fill="#a1a1aa" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Risk sits on: bank balance sheet</text>
      <text x="178" y="206" fill="#38bdf8" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Backstop: capital rules · central bank</text>
      <rect x="372" y="82" width="300" height="150" rx="10" fill="#2a1616" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.6"/>
      <text x="522" y="108" fill="#fecaca" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700">Tokenized (atomic settlement)</text>
      <text x="522" y="134" fill="#fca5a5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Trade = Settle (at once, final)</text>
      <text x="522" y="158" fill="#fca5a5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Time to intervene ≈ 0</text>
      <text x="522" y="182" fill="#fca5a5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Risk sits on: code · platforms · oracles</text>
      <text x="522" y="206" fill="#fca5a5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">Backstop: unclear</text>
      <line x1="330" y1="157" x2="370" y2="157" stroke="#a1a1aa" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#ar1e)"/>
      <defs><marker id="ar1e" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="8" refX="6" refY="4" orient="auto"><path d="M0,0 L8,4 L0,8 z" fill="#a1a1aa"/></marker></defs>
      <rect x="28" y="252" width="644" height="120" rx="10" fill="#0f2e2a" stroke="#14b8a6" stroke-width="1.4"/>
      <text x="350" y="278" fill="#5eead4" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700">The two fracture points the IMF names</text>
      <text x="350" y="306" fill="#e4e4e7" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">1. Liquidity fragmentation — isolated pools across incompatible platforms</text>
      <text x="350" y="330" fill="#e4e4e7" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">2. Real-time cross-border flow — supervisors' response time erased</text>
      <text x="350" y="356" fill="#a1a1aa" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13">RWA ex-stablecoins ~$6.5B → $26B (1yr, +300%)</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  </div>
